name: Cinemabase.GitHub.io
body:
### Welcome to CinemaBase.
```
Android mobile application which allows you to 
browse ratings and descriptions of current top rated movies or 
search through movie database to 
find ratings and description of favorite movie titles. 
Find out what friends are saying about currently rated movies, and 
give your own thoughts about movies you have watched.
```
### Authors and Contributors
Daniel Hernandez (@dehernandez7791), and Victor Romero (@romero4742), 
Computer Science students Cal Polytechnic Pomona.
